{"tid":108540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【教書教上床】打野戰 出國交歡 索Miss認偷嗒學生但唔使坐監？","createTime":"2017-02-05T10:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T12:55:13.000Z","uid":29627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4acf886b00db0e6b73cdeeac4e24e4773c34ef71","tid":108540,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"【教書教上床】打野戰 出國交歡 索Miss認偷嗒學生但唔使坐監？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170205/large/1486264470_45a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170205%2Flarge%2F1486264470_45a1.jpg&h=5845545a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 美國德州一名29歲女教師，先後搭上2名未成年男學生並發生性關係，她與其中一人的交歡次數更多達10次。她早前承認兩項與青少年發生不當行為罪，法官將在下月判刑，代表律師估計她會被判感化、不會入獄亦不用列入性罪犯名單。<br />\n<br />\n案情指29歲的韋爾（Haeli Wey），前年6月與未成年男學生在一個學生計劃中認識，並與他及其家人赴南非交流，期間兩人發生性關係。兩人的關係維持了2個月，直至男生得悉韋爾與另一男生行山，於是向家人透露事件，家人報警。<br />\n<br />\n另一名17歲男生就指，與韋爾行山期間她取出吊床，兩人在吊床上做愛。他又坦言一早料到會與韋爾做愛，因為「老師不會相約學生外出」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170205/56263439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170205%2F56263439&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP98VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3a79b246\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170205%2F56263439&h=eaa079ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170205/56263439</a>"},{"pid":"2263e8de4360bf54af445a3c1e404374d141afac","tid":108540,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"快點強姦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a081ad4d384fb8ecaee2f3129a0fd8728a4417","tid":108540,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:25:57.000Z","msg":"Why沒